Constructor __construct (line 62)

Create Gdata_Calendar_EventQuery object. If a URL is provided,

it becomes the base URL, and additional URL components may be appended. For instance, if $url is 'http://www.foo.com', the default URL constructed will be 'http://www.foo.com/default/public/full'
